DBsheetConfig.query: SELECT T1.CurveId, T1.GroupingId, T1.CurveDescription, T5.value VolatilityType, T6.value Extrapolation, T7.value DayCounter, T8.value Dimension, T9.value Calendar, T10.value BusinessDayConvention, T1.OptionTenors, T1.SwapTenors, T1.SmileOptionTenors, T1.SmileSwapTenors, T1.SmileSpreads, T16.value ShortSwapIndexBase, T17.value SwapIndexBase FROM ORE.dbo.CurveConfigurationSwaptionVolatilities T1 INNER JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesVolatilityType T5 ON T1.VolatilityType = T5.value LEFT JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesExtrapolationType T6 ON T1.Extrapolation = T6.value LEFT JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesDayCounter T7 ON T1.DayCounter = T7.value INNER JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesDimensionType T8 ON T1.Dimension = T8.value LEFT JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesCalendar T9 ON T1.Calendar = T9.value INNER JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesBusinessDayConvention T10 ON T1.BusinessDayConvention = T10.value INNER JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesIndexName T16 ON T1.ShortSwapIndexBase = T16.value INNER JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesIndexName T17 ON T1.SwapIndexBase = T17.value

field.name: VolatilityType
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value VolatilityType,!T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesVolatilityType !T! ORDER BY !T!.value

field.name: Extrapolation
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value Extrapolation,!T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesExtrapolationType !T! ORDER BY !T!.value

field.name: DayCounter
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value DayCounter, !T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesDayCounter !T! ORDER BY value

field.name: Dimension
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value Dimension,!T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesDimensionType !T! ORDER BY !T!.value

field.name: Calendar
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value Calendar,!T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesCalendar !T! ORDER BY value

field.name: BusinessDayConvention
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value BusinessDayConvention,!T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesBusinessDayConvention !T! ORDER BY !T!.value

field.name: ShortSwapIndexBase
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value ShortSwapIndexBase,!T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesIndexName !T! ORDER BY !T!.value

field.name: SwapIndexBase
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value SwapIndexBase,!T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesIndexName !T! ORDER BY !T!.value
